data.description: Welcome to your new haven in Bloomingdale—a stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that exudes warmth and charm. As you step inside, the exquisite tile flooring throughout the living area catches your eye, setting a tone of elegance and comfort.    To the left of the entrance, you'll find the dining area, strategically placed for easy access to the well-appointed kitchen. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring a convenient walk-in pantry to cater to all your storage needs. On the right side upon entering, a versatile room awaits, ready to be transformed into a cozy sitting room, den, or whatever suits your lifestyle.    The split concept of this home unveils a master bedroom adorned with laminate flooring and a fully remodeled walk-in bathroom—a private retreat offering both style and functionality. The other two bedrooms also boast laminate flooring and share a recently remodeled second bathroom, adding a touch of contemporary luxury to the home.    Custom blinds grace all rooms, providing a touch of personalization and privacy. The front windows are equipped with hurricane shutters, offering both protection and peace of mind. Step out into the backyard, and you'll discover a true oasis. Adorned with vibrant flowers, a starfruit tree, a guava tree, and a banana tree, the yard is a haven for nature enthusiasts.    Recent additions include gutters that enhance the functionality and aesthetics of the home. The HVAC system was thoughtfully replaced in 2021, ensuring your comfort throughout the seasons. Notably, this residence is situated in a community with NO HOA AND NO CDD fees—granting you the freedom to bring your boat, RV, trailer, or any other recreational vehicles and securely park them in the fully fenced backyard.    Welcome home to the perfect blend of style, functionality, and freedom. This Bloomingdale gem is more than just a house; it's a canvas for you to paint the lifestyle you've always dreamed of.    Conveniently nestled near Bloomingdale Park, this home offers not only a picturesque setting but also immediate access to a range of recreational amenities. Bloomingdale Park, just a stone's throw away, becomes an extension of your backyard, offering a playground for the little ones, basketball and tennis courts for sports enthusiasts, volleyball for some friendly competition, and more.    The location further enhances the appeal of this residence with seamless access to a variety of stores and amenities, ensuring that daily conveniences are within easy reach. Whether you're looking for shopping, dining, or entertainment options, the proximity to I-75 adds an additional layer of convenience, making commuting a breeze and opening up a world of possibilities just a short drive away.    Discover the perfect blend of a tranquil home life and the vibrancy of nearby attractions. Welcome to a residence that not only provides comfort within its walls but also opens doors to a community rich in recreational opportunities and convenience.
